						<p>Slab in the Archaeological Museum.</p>						

						<p>1500 A.D. [15th century A.D.]</p>						

						<p>The record is dated Śaka 1422, Siddhārthin, Bhādrapada ba. 3. Seems to describe the arrangment made for the cultivation of fallow land, <hi rend="italic">etc.,</hi> under specified conditions, when Khaneajamamutabāṅe-mojama Gālibakhāna was holding charge of the Thāne-mamale Mahamudābāda.</p>						

